.TH origin-hints 1  "origin-hints " 
.SH NAME
origin\-hints \- DNS hints for `origin_bypass` (authorized targets only)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBorigin\-hints\fR <\fB\-\-host\fR> [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
DNS hints for `origin_bypass` (authorized targets only)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-host\fR \fI<HOST>\fR
Hostname only (e.g. `api.example.com`), not a full URL
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR [default: text]
`text` or `json`
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
text
.IP \(bu 2
json
.RE
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
